        <h2 style="margin-top:0;">Hi, I'm Nichole! 👋</h2>
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.7;">I'm a mom of five (including twins!), a former speech-language pathologist (MS, CCC-SLP), and a renewable energy enthusiast. After a decade in pediatric therapy, I became a stay-at-home mom and discovered a passion for sustainable living and energy independence.</p>
      </div>
